# Coursera session credentials
# Required only for the GraphQL search scraper (scripts/coursera.py).
# The REST catalog scraper does NOT need these.
#
# How to obtain (Chrome, while logged in to coursera.org):
#
#   CAUTH
#     DevTools (F12) > Application tab > Cookies > www.coursera.org
#     Find the "CAUTH" row and copy the Value column.
#
#   CSRF3_TOKEN
#     DevTools (F12) > Network tab > filter by "graphql-gateway"
#     Click any request > Headers > find "x-csrf3-token" and copy its value.
#
# Tokens expire after ~24 hours. Re-copy from the browser when they do.

CAUTH=
CSRF3_TOKEN=
